dots
====
This repository contains my personal NixOS configuration and dotfiles.
The goal is a minimal, reproducible, and developer-focused Linux setup.

System Overview
===============
OS: NixOS (flakes-enabled)
Shell: Bash
Terminal: kitty
Window system: X11 (dwm)
Editor: Neovim

Notes
=====
These configs are tailored for my hardware and workflow.
Use at your own risk.
Expect breaking changes.
